6月末，巴哈马东北方向的中层[[低压槽|低压槽]]和[[东风波|东风波]]相互影响，形成本季第一个获命名的热带气旋。到了6月30日，系统内已明显存在层次分明的环流，卫星图像还显示气旋拥有[[雨带|带状特征]]。<ref name="ATCR" />次日，系统成为热带低气压<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = Hurricane Specialists Unit | publisher = National Hurricane Center | year = 2009 | accessdate = 2017-01-16 | title = Easy to Read HURDAT 1851-2008 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305031132/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html }}</ref>，并且不久后就因[[飓风猎人|侦察机]]测得烈风强度风速而升级成热带风暴。受东侧的[[高气压|高气压区]]影响，爱丽丝总体保持北上趋势，并因[[风切变|风切变]]减少而逐渐组织，到7月3日已发展出层次分明的[[风眼|风眼]]。侦察机此时已确认气旋达到飓风标准，最大持续风速提升到每小时130公里。<ref name="ATCR" />

7月4日，风暴东侧风眼墙掠过[[百慕大|百慕大]]，在此期间达到持续风速每小时150公里、最低[[气压|气压]]986[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.11[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度。经过百慕大后，爱丽丝开始因[[美国东部|美国东部]]上空的中层低压槽影响而加快移动速度并减弱。7月6日，气旋逼近加拿大大西洋省份，风速已降至热带风暴水平。<ref name="ATCR" />当晚，风暴以风力时速95公里强度登陆[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]东部<ref name="HURDAT" />，然后转变成温带气旋<ref name="ATCR" />。

经过百慕大期间，飓风产生的持续风速为每小时120公里，阵风时速140公里<ref name="ATCR" /><ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | work = Pittsburgh Post-Gazette | date = 1973-07-04 | accessdate = 2017-01-20 | title = Hurricane Alice Nears Bermuda | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=lQIOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=LW0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=3165,284042&dq=hurricane+alice+1973 | archive-date = 2021-11-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211125112944/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=lQIOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=LW0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=3165%2C284042&dq=hurricane+alice+1973 }}</ref>。岛上没有经受严重破坏，只有部分树木倒塌，输电线缆中断<ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | title = Hurricane Alice Hits Bermuda | date = 1973-07-04 | newspaper = The Aiken Standard | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/3605840/aiken_standard/ | accessdate = 2017-01-20 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2016-03-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160321231220/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/3605840/aiken_standard/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。百慕大降下暴雨<ref name="TL1">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | publisher = The Ledger | date = 1973-07-04 | accessdate = 2017-01-20 | title = Hurricane Alice Leaves Bermuda Mostly Unhurt | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=IScVAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Z_oDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5655,939498&dq=hurricane+alice+1973 | archive-date = 2021-11-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211125112944/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=IScVAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Z_oDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5655%2C939498&dq=hurricane+alice+1973 }}</ref>，最高降雨量为116毫米<ref name="WPCMAX">{{cite book | last = Roth | first = David M. | date = 2015-04-29 | accessdate = 2017-01-21 | chapter-url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmaxima.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160120194350/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmaxima.html | archivedate = 2016-01-20 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcrainfall.html | publisher = United States Weather Prediction Center | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Data | chapter = Tropical Cyclone Point Maxima }}</ref>，为岛上持续三个月的旱情划上句点<ref name="TL1" />。虽然爱丽丝一度经过加拿大大西洋省份<ref name="ATCR" />，但没有任何记载表明当地因此受到影响<ref name="CHC73">{{cite web | publisher = Canadian Hurricane Centre | date = 2007-07-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161117191725/http://www.ec.gc.ca/ouragans-hurricanes/default.asp?lang=En&n=6A91A374-1 | accessdate = 2017-01-21 | title = Canadian Tropical Cyclone Season Summary for 1973 | archivedate = 2016-11-17 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.ec.gc.ca/ouragans-hurricanes/default.asp?lang=en&n=6A91A374-1 }}</ref>。
