7月下旬，[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]][[哈特拉斯角_(北卡罗莱纳州)|哈特拉斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Hatteras}}）形成[[冷心低压|冷芯]]上层低气压区并向南移动。系统环流逐渐下沉，发展出[[亚热带气旋|亚热带天气系统特征]]。7月31日，系统在[[中大西洋地区|中大西洋地区]]近海达到烈风强度并获名“阿尔法”，是本季首场获命名的亚热带风暴。气旋朝[[罗盘方位|东北偏北]]方向沿海岸线平行移动，强度在此期间基本保持稳定。到了8月1日，系统强度已在逼近[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]期间降至低于亚热带风暴标准，最终于8月2日在[[缅因州|缅因州]]南岸近海消散。<ref name="ATCR" />

阿尔法在新英格兰降下小到中雨，其中[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]][[富兰克林县_(马萨诸塞州)|富兰克林县]]的[[特纳斯福尔斯_(马萨诸塞州)|特纳斯福尔斯]]（{{lang|en|Turners Falls}}）降雨量最高，达128毫米。缅因州南部大部分地区测得约25毫米雨量，<ref>{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2009 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304084513/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/alfa1973.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2017-01-21 | title = Subtropical Storm Alfa —July 31 – August 2, 1973 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/alfa1973.html }}</ref>其中又以[[索科_(缅因州)|索科]]最高，有66毫米<ref name="New Eng">{{cite book | last1 = Roth | first1 = David M | author2 = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2012 | chapter = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall for the New England United States | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Point Maxima | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050333/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcnewengland.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2017-01-22 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcnewengland.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。
