{{Main article|1973年飓风布伦达}}
飓风布伦达源自8月9日离开非洲西岸的东风波，起初进入大西洋后呈快速减弱趋势。到了8月13日，东风波已在途经[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]期间开始再生，数天后，系统关联的对流聚拢成中心<ref name="ATCR" />，经过充分组织而于8月18日在[[尤卡坦海峡|尤卡坦海峡]]附近成为热带低气压<ref name="HURDAT" />。次日清晨，气旋强化成热带风暴并获名“布伦达”（{{lang|en|Brenda}}），随即登陆[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]北部。系统向内陆行进，并因德克萨斯州上空的强劲高压脊转向西南，于8月20日进入[[坎佩切湾|坎佩切湾]]。<ref name="ATCR" />

回到海上后，风暴又开始增强，于8月20日晚成为飓风。次日，布伦达发展出层次分明的[[风眼|风眼]]，达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]150公里、最低气压977毫巴（百帕，28.85英寸汞柱）的最高强度，在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下接近一级飓风上限。气旋当晚以最高强度从墨西哥[[卡门城|卡门城]]附近登陆，成为有纪录以来首场直接袭击坎佩切州的飓风。气旋进入陆地上空后迅速减弱，于8月22日早上降级成热带低气压，并在当天消散。<ref name="ATCR" />

墨西哥此前已经受到严重洪灾摧残，导致至少18人死亡，20万人流离失所，布伦达来袭后降下瓢泼大雨并引发洪灾，令灾情雪上加霜<ref name="LAT1">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 1973-08-20 | accessdate = 2017-01-16 | title = Hurricane Brenda Heightens Flooding Misery in Mexico | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/doc/157347995.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Aug%2020,%201973&author=&pub=Los%20Angeles%20Times&edition=&startpage=&desc=Hurricane%20Brenda%20Heightens%20Flooding%20Misery%20in%20Mexico | archive-date = 2017-12-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171216144054/https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/doc/157347995.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Aug%2020,%201973&author=&pub=Los%20Angeles%20Times&edition=&startpage=&desc=Hurricane%20Brenda%20Heightens%20Flooding%20Misery%20in%20Mexico | dead-url = no }}</ref>。气旋至少夺走该国十条人命<ref name="ATCR" />。飓风过去后，该国又遭遇重大[[地震|地震]]，致使大量建筑倒塌，救灾工作受阻<ref>{{cite news | author = Francis B. Kent | publisher = [[洛杉矶时报|Los Angeles Times]] | date = 1973-08-30 | accessdate = 2017-01-16 | title = Torrential Rains Hamper Hunt for Quake Victims in Mexico | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/doc/157315437.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Aug%2030,%201973&author=&pub=Los%20Angeles%20Times&edition=&startpage=&desc=Torrential%20Rains%20Hamper%20Hunt%20for%20Quake%20Victims%20in%20Mexico | archive-date = 2017-12-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171217014032/https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/doc/157315437.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Aug%2030,%201973&author=&pub=Los%20Angeles%20Times&edition=&startpage=&desc=Torrential%20Rains%20Hamper%20Hunt%20for%20Quake%20Victims%20in%20Mexico | dead-url = no }}</ref>。风暴期间，陆地上的阵风时速高达180公里，造成严重破坏。[[坎佩切|坎佩切]]约八成城区被淹，且有两人丧生。<ref name="SPT1" />沿海城市[[韦拉克鲁斯_(韦拉克鲁斯州)|韦拉克鲁斯]]遭遇25年间最严重的洪灾。受气旋直接影响，该国估计有2000人无家可归。<ref name="ATCR" />一艘载有25人的货轮遭遇风暴后发动机失灵，被困在海上<ref name="SPT1">{{cite web | author = United Press International | publisher = St. Petersburg Times | date = 1973-08-22 | accessdate = 2017-01-20 | title = Brenda Sloshes Into Mexico; 2 Persons Killed | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=BcANAAAAIBAJ&sjid=-HIDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6895,624077&dq=hurricane+brenda+1973 | archive-date = 2021-11-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211119042026/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=BcANAAAAIBAJ&sjid=-HIDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6895%2C624077&dq=hurricane+brenda+1973 }}</ref>，直到气旋进入墨西哥湾后才获救<ref name="ATCR" />。
