受德克萨斯州东南部上空的热带风暴迪莉娅影响，加勒比海西北部上空存在东南走向的低压槽。9月6日，这片低压槽内发展出热带低气压。气旋强度偏弱，于9月10日抵达德克萨斯州海岸，并在登陆后降下暴雨，造成重大破坏，气象机构在实际操作中把这些破坏视为热带风暴迪莉娅引起。<ref name="ATCR" />转向东北进入内陆上空后，热带低气压的移动速度大幅提升，最终于9月14日在北卡罗莱纳州上空逐渐消散<ref name="HPCTD11">{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2009 | accessdate = 2017-01-24 | title = Tropical Depression Eleven — September 8–14, 1973 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304042816/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/td11aof1973.html | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/td11aof1973.html }}</ref>。

气旋在德克萨斯州和路易斯安那州沿海地区降下暴雨，弗里波特附近雨量最高，达283毫米<ref name="HPCTD11" />。路易斯安那州南部多地降雨量在130毫米以上，其中最高的[[金德_(路易斯安那州)|金德]]有230毫米<ref name="HPCGC">{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2009 | accessdate = 2017-01-25 | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall for the Gulf Coast | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304092617/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcgulfcoast.html | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcgulfcoast.html }}</ref>。南、北卡罗莱纳州和乔治亚州降水也很可观，多地雨量超过76毫米<ref name="HPCTD11" />，其中南卡罗莱纳州[[惠特迈尔_(南卡罗莱纳州)|惠特迈尔]]附近最高，为237毫米<ref name="WPCSE">{{cite book | last = Roth | first = David M | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Point Maxima | chapter = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall in the Southeastern United States | author2 = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070229/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcsoutheast.html | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcsoutheast.html | accessdate = 2017-01-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。整场风暴一共对路易斯安那州南部的农作物造成2200万美元损失<ref name="ATCR" /><ref>{{cite web | author = Andrew A. Yemma | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | date = 1973-09-06 | accessdate = 2017-01-20 | title = Delia Threatens Grain Crops | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=c70NAAAAIBAJ&sjid=_HIDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6973,3612610&dq=tropical+storm+delia+damage | archive-date = 2021-11-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211119051830/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=c70NAAAAIBAJ&sjid=_HIDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6973%2C3612610&dq=tropical+storm+delia+damage }}</ref>。
