9月24日，巴哈马东北方向形成低气压<ref name="HPCTD13" />。次日，美国国家飓风中心发布首份公告，宣布系统属亚热带低气压。气旋结构很不对称，风力主要集中在中心以北约480公里位置<ref name="TD13B1">{{cite web | author = Robert Simpson | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1973-09-25 | accessdate = 2017-01-25 | title = Subtropical Depression Thirteen Bulletin One | archivedate = 2020-08-27 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200827211414/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0177-jpg/1973/atlantic/td%2326/public/pub252100z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0177-jpg/1973/atlantic/td%2326/public/pub252100z.jpg }}</ref>。当晚，亚热带低气压转变成热带低气压，气象机构还向北卡罗莱纳州至佛罗里达州[[圣奥古斯丁_(佛罗里达州)|圣奥古斯丁]]沿海地区发布小型船只公告<ref>{{cite web | author = Joseph Pelissier | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1973-09-25 | accessdate = 2017-01-25 | title = Tropical Depression Thirteen Bulletin Two | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200827214208/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0177-jpg/1973/atlantic/td%2326/public/pub260200z.jpg | archivedate = 2020-08-27 | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0177-jpg/1973/atlantic/td%2326/public/pub260200z.jpg }}</ref>。受北侧[[副热带高压脊|副热带高压脊]]的薄弱环节影响，气旋朝西北偏北移动，然后从佛罗里达州[[马林兰_(佛罗里达州)|马林兰]]附近登陆并迅速减弱，最终在抵达墨西哥湾前逐渐消散<ref name="HPCTD13">{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2009 | accessdate = 2017-01-25 | title = Tropical Depression Thirteen — September 23–27, 1973 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/td13aof1973.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304053135/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/td13aof1973.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | format = JPG }}</ref>。

受气旋影响，佛罗里达州和乔治亚州部分地区降下暴雨，并以[[奥兰多_(佛罗里达州)|奥兰多]]雨量最高，约为171毫米，另有多地雨量在76毫米以上<ref name="HPCTD13" />。部分地点阵风时速达到65公里<ref>{{cite web | author = Herbert Saffir | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1973-09-27 | accessdate = 2017-01-25 | title = Tropical Depression Thirteen Bulletin Four (Final) | archivedate = 2020-08-27 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200827230059/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0177-jpg/1973/atlantic/td%2326/public/pub261330z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0177-jpg/1973/atlantic/td%2326/public/pub261330z.jpg }}</ref>。风暴在海上产生三米大浪，多艘船只受影响<ref name="TD13B1" />。南卡罗莱纳州部分地区发生轻度海滩侵蚀和沿海洪灾<ref>{{cite web | author = National Weather Service in Charleston, South Carolina | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1973-09-26 | accessdate = 2017-01-25 | title = South Carolina Special Tide Statement September 26, 1973 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0177-jpg/1973/atlantic/td%2326/local/chs260200z.jpg | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200827214212/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0177-jpg/1973/atlantic/td%2326/local/chs260200z.jpg | archivedate = 2020-08-27 | deadurl = no | format = JPG }}</ref>。乔治亚州部分沿海地区因大浪导致道路封闭，还有部分民居被淹。[[萨凡纳|萨凡纳]]警方通报称大浪越过部分海堤，但没有造成破坏<ref>{{cite web | author = National Weather Service in Savannah, Georgia | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1973-09-26 | accessdate = 2017-01-25 | title = Georgia Special Tide Statement September 26, 1973 | archivedate = 2020-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200827231701/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0177-jpg/1973/atlantic/td%2326/local/sav260300z.jpg | deadurl = no | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0177-jpg/1973/atlantic/td%2326/local/sav260300z.jpg }}</ref>。
